AM_PROG_LIBTOOL

dnl
dnl Detect the canonical host and target build environment
dnl
AC_CANONICAL_HOST
AC_CANONICAL_TARGET

dnl Checks for programs.
AC_PROG_CC

dnl Check for AIX weirdos
